---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="For Hotel Owners - DayDreamHub" description="List your hotel on DayDreamHub and connect with travelers across Asia looking for day-use stays.">

<section class="bg-teal-50 py-16 sm:py-24"> <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center"> <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
Take Your Facility and Services to the World!
</h1> <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
Join DayDreamHub and connect your property with travelers from across Asia looking for day-use stays.
</p> <a href="/owner-application-form" class="btn-primary text-lg px-10 py-4 inline-block font-semibold">
List Your Room
</a> </div> </section>  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16"> <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6"> <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 text-center">
About DayDreamHub
</h2> <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
DayDreamHub is Asia's first online travel agency (OTA) specializing in day-use hotel stays.
        We connect property owners with a growing base of travelers seeking short-term accommodations
        for transit, business, personal breaks, and daycation experiences.
</p> </div> </section>  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-gray-50"> <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6"> <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">
Why List on DayDreamHub?
</h2> <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6"> <!-- Zero Listing Fees --> <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center"> <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5"> <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-teal-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path> </svg> </div> <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Zero Listing Fees</h3> <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
No initial costs to get started. We only charge a commission on completed bookings -- you pay nothing until you earn.
</p> </div> <!-- Open Listing Policy --> <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center"> <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5"> <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-teal-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"> <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path> </svg> </div> <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Open Listing Policy</h3> <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
Corporations and individual property owners are all welcome. Whether you manage a hotel chain or a single room, we'd love to have you.
</p> </div> </div> </div> </section>  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16"> <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6"> <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-10 text-center">
Registration Process
</h2> <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6"> <div class="text-center"> <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-teal-700 text-white text-xl font-bold flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"> 1 </div> <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Sign Up</h3> <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Complete the application form with your property details.</p> </div><div class="text-center"> <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-teal-700 text-white text-xl font-bold flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"> 2 </div> <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Identity Verification</h3> <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Required for individual owners and companies registering without a prior appointment. Submit your ID or business documents for review.</p> </div><div class="text-center"> <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-teal-700 text-white text-xl font-bold flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"> 3 </div> <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Registration Complete</h3> <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Receive your credentials via email once approved.</p> </div><div class="text-center"> <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-teal-700 text-white text-xl font-bold flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4"> 4 </div> <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Start Listing</h3> <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Log in and begin listing your rooms to welcome guests.</p> </div> </div> <!-- Connector line (visible on large screens) --> <div class="hidden lg:block relative -mt-[7.5rem] mb-[5.5rem] mx-auto" style="width: calc(100% - 8rem);"> <div class="border-t-2 border-dashed border-gray-200"></div> </div> </div> </section>  <section id="register" class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-teal-50"> <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center"> <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
List your facility on DayDreamHub and welcome guests from around the world!
</h2> <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
Get started today and turn your empty rooms into revenue.
</p> <a href="/owner-application-form" class="btn-primary text-lg px-10 py-4 inline-block font-semibold">
List Your Room
</a> <p class="mt-6 text-gray-500 text-sm">
Or contact us via the <a href="/contact" class="text-teal-700 hover:underline font-medium">contact form</a>.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 text-xs">
          By registering, you agree to our
          <a href="/owner-terms" class="text-teal-600 hover:underline">Owner Terms of Service</a>
          ・
          <a href="/ja/owner-terms" class="text-teal-600 hover:underline">オーナー利用規約</a>
        </p>
 </div> </section>


</Layout>
